{"tid":928331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【走塑】南韓研發大米及木薯製飲管 可喝凍熱飲亦可直接食用","createTime":"2018-12-04T18:12:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T06:57:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":331,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"3e7e6a9ea6bceb9d74c5c9fb3a291895c831c24a","tid":928331,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T18:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181204/large/1543929018_de3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181204%2Flarge%2F1543929018_de3c.jpg&h=350b2636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓自今年8月起推出限塑令，禁止客人在店內使用即棄用品，只能在外賣時使用。繼台灣研發的可分解甘蔗渣飲管，南韓最近有公司成功研發新飲管，由含70%的大米，30%的木薯所造，不但飲管凍熱飲皆宜，可浸泡在熱飲使用約2至3小時，亦可直接吃掉。據悉，該新飲管成份除了大米外，還有製作珍珠奶茶的珍珠材料，即木薯，表面光滑，亦有韌性，與一般飲管的使用感很相似。現時新飲管已大量生產，單月產量達3億支，一支批發價約為1元，價格便宜，正計劃在上百家咖啡店和部份高端酒店供貨。此外，南韓近年追上全球減塑風潮，越來越多店家採用環保吸管，而目標是創造更多好吃的吸管，像是含有維他命紅蔘和甲殼素，可以吸引更多老人家和民眾。<br />\n記者：何嘉茵"},{"pid":"71767d71315ec6b83fa3f53e38a461ba360aa930","tid":928331,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T18:19:34.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"70da3b2e4f4afbcfe0144acc9c69b13ced71bfea","tid":928331,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"71767d71315ec6b83fa3f53e38a461ba360aa930","tid":928331,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T18:19:34.000Z","msg":"Link?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T18:20:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20181205/58992747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181205%2F58992747&d=OdK%2BOMrWUmYXEJLOqe%2BELS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=e083b526\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181205%2F58992747&h=4d255036\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realti